Arsenal legend, Paul Merson has predicted the outcome of the Premier League match-day 34 fixtures taking place this weekend. Arsenal will host Manchester United in a Premier League tie at Emirates Stadium on Saturday afternoon, while Leicester City will tackle Aston Villa at the King Power Stadium. Manchester City will face Watford at Etihad Stadium on Saturday, while Chelsea will clash with West Ham United on Sunday afternoon at Stamford Bridge. Providing his predictions, Merson was quoted by Sportskeeda as saying: Arsenal 2-2 Manchester United
Leicester City 1-2 Aston Villa
Manchester City 5-0 Watford
Norwich City 2-2 Newcastle United
Brentford 2-1 Tottenham Hotspur
Burnley 1-0 Wolverhampton Wanderers
Chelsea 2-0 West Ham United
Brighton & Hove Albion 2-0 Southampton
Liverpool 3-0 Everton
Crystal Palace 2-0 Leeds United